{"_response_info":{"status":"ok"},"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/report-debris-motorways-main-roads.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/report-debris-motorways-main-roads","title":"Report debris and litter on motorways and main roads","format":"answer","updated_at":"2013-01-09T13:00:05+00:00","details":{"need_id":"2528","business_proposition":false,"description":"Reporting obstructions or debris on trunk roads, A roads, major routes, motorways across the UK - phone numbers","language":"en","body":"\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>If you see debris or an obstruction on an A road or motorway in England, Scotland or Wales, report it by phone.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice help-notice\">\n<p>Never use your <a href=\"/using-mobile-phones-when-driving-the-law\" title=\"Using mobile phones when driving\">mobile phone while driving.</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Motorways and main roads</h2>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>Highways Agency (England)</strong> <br />\n0300 123 5000<br />\n24 hours, 7 days a week</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>Traffic Scotland</strong><br />\n0800 028 1414<br />\n24 hours, 7 days a week</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>Traffic Wales</strong><br />\n0845 602 6020<br />\n24 hours, 7 days a week</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>In Northern Ireland, contact the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.nidirect.gov.uk/report-a-problem-with-the-roads\" title=\"Contact the Department for Regional Development\">Department for Regional Development</a></p>\n\n<h2>Local roads</h2>\n<p>Report <a href=\"/reporting-road-obstruction\" title=\"Report litter and debris\">litter and debris</a> and <a href=\"/report-abandoned-vehicle\" title=\"Report an abandoned vehicle\">abandoned vehicles</a> to your local council. </p>\n","alternative_title":""},"tags":[{"title":"Recycling, rubbish, streets and roads","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/housing%2Frecycling-rubbish.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Information about r